   "source": [
    "# Session 5\n",
    "\n",
    "## Alternative approach to solving elliptic equations"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# We always start with appropriate imports; note the use of the IPython magic\n",
    "# command to set up Matplotlib within the notebook\n",
    "%matplotlib inline\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Question 1\n",
    "\n",
    "We start with the basic Jacobi solver for completeness"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def update_phi(phi, N):\n",
    "    \"\"\"Update NxN grid of phi using Jacobi method\"\"\"\n",
    "    phiout = np.copy(phi)\n",
    "    for i in range(1,N-1):\n",
    "        for j in range(1,N-1):\n",
    "            phiout[i,j] = 0.25*(phi[i-1,j] + phi[i+1,j] \n",
    "                              + phi[i,j-1] + phi[i,j+1])\n",
    "    return phiout"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def update_phi_GS(phi, N):\n",
    "    \"\"\"Update NxN grid of phi using Gauss-Seidel method\"\"\"\n",
    "    for i in range(1,N-1):\n",
    "        for j in range(1,N-1):\n",
    "            phi[i,j] = 0.25*(phi[i-1,j] + phi[i+1,j] + phi[i,j-1] + phi[i,j+1])\n",
    "    return phi"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def update_phi_GS_SOR(phi, N, omega):\n",
    "    \"\"\"Update NxN grid of phi using SOR and Gauss-Seidel\"\"\"\n",
    "    for i in range(1,N-1):\n",
    "        for j in range(1,N-1):\n",
    "            phi[i,j] = (1.0+omega)*0.25*(phi[i-1,j] + phi[i+1,j] + phi[i,j-1] + phi[i,j+1]) - omega*phi[i,j]\n",
    "    return phi"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Question 2"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "N = 15\n",
    "phi = np.ones((N,N))\n",
    "phi *= 3.0\n",
    "phi[0,:] = 3\n",
    "phi[N-1,:] = 3\n",
    "phi[:,0] = 4\n",
    "phi[:,N-1] = 4\n",
    "phi[0,0] = 3.5\n",
    "phi[0,N-1] = 3.5\n",
    "phi[N-1,0] =  3.5\n",
    "phi[N-1,N-1] = 3.5"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "Finished after  121  iterations\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "tol = 1e-4\n",
    "delta = 1.0\n",
    "iter = 1\n",
    "while delta > tol:\n",
    "    phiin = np.copy(phi)\n",
    "    phi = update_phi_GS(phi,N)\n",
    "    delta = np.max(np.abs(phiin - phi))\n",
    "    iter += 1\n",
    "print(\"Finished after \",iter,\" iterations\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Question 3"

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Question 4"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "With omega= 0.1  finished after  102  iterations\n",
      "With omega= 0.3  finished after  72  iterations\n",
      "With omega= 0.5  finished after  47  iterations\n",
      "With omega= 0.7  finished after  32  iterations\n",
      "With omega= 0.9  finished after  90  iterations\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "N = 15\n",
    "for omega in (0.1,0.3,0.5,0.7,0.9):\n",
    "    phi_om0p1 = np.ones((N,N))\n",
    "    phi_om0p1 *= 3.0\n",
    "    phi_om0p1[0,:] = 3\n",
    "    phi_om0p1[N-1,:] = 3\n",
    "    phi_om0p1[:,0] = 4\n",
    "    phi_om0p1[:,N-1] = 4\n",
    "    phi_om0p1[0,0] = 3.5\n",
    "    phi_om0p1[0,N-1] = 3.5\n",
    "    phi_om0p1[N-1,0] =  3.5\n",
    "    phi_om0p1[N-1,N-1] = 3.5\n",
    "    tol = 1e-4\n",
    "    delta = 1.0\n",
    "    iter = 1\n",
    "    while delta > tol:\n",
    "        phiin = np.copy(phi_om0p1)\n",
    "        phi_om0p1 = update_phi_GS_SOR(phi_om0p1,N,omega)\n",
    "        delta = np.max(np.abs(phiin - phi_om0p1))\n",
    "        iter += 1\n",
    "    print(\"With omega=\",omega,\" finished after \",iter,\" iterations\")"
   ]
  },
